The '''Big Nasty Free-For-All''' was a competition held by the [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]] as a test of skill for warriors. Events included the [[Gullipud|gulli]]-brawl, gulli-throw, and a race through the ocean. [[Rugor Nass/Legends|Rugor Nass]] won this competition a record three times in a row.

